data.description: Small town living in a comfortable split level with beautiful farmhouse touches awaits your personal updates! Located in a quiet neighborhood off of downtown Galesville across from a park, this 3 bed 2 bath home is perfect for first time buyers and families alike. Featuring 2 bedrooms and 1 full bathroom on the main level and 1 bedroom and 1 bath on the lower level, newer finishes are spread throughout - light fixtures, appliances, flooring, and paint. The lower level boasts a large family room with a pellet stove to keep warm in the cold Wisconsin winter. The upper level deck offers a great outdoor space to relax. Numerous, large windows let in ample natural light. The spacious 1 car garage is attached to the main entry with access to the back yard. Take the scenic drive to see today!
